OL,3,CCommissioner denies blocking scrutiny
OL,4,Cover day centre closures
OL,6,FITV News Central's Political Reporter
OL,7,FLewis Warner speaks to the unelected
OL,8,Fman overseeing Birmingham City
OL,9,FCouncil, as he defends his decision to
OL,10,Foverrule councillors on controversial
OL,11,Fcuts
OL,13,FMax Caller, Lead Commissioner for
OL,14,FBirmingham City Council, has denied
OL,15,Fblocking democratic scrutiny over a
OL,16,Fdecision to close four adult day
OL,17,Fcentres.
